metadata.description:
ABBIE - Entity N° 0008  
Mitch Myers b.1989

Tether Resides in the Phase of: Silence

A space of suffocating introspection and self-doubt. Created by the experiences of being unheard, disregarded, or silenced by the reality around you. This Tether holds the weight of secrets, regrets, and unfulfilled desires. Those who are bound to this Tether may feel that they are drowning in their own thoughts and feelings, unable to express themselves or to connect with others, and that their silence is a burden that will never be lifted.

[ +PFP of Artwork Will Airdrop To Collectors Wallet ]
